item.title: YOU GUYS ARE ALL TERRIBLE AND WILL EVENTUALLY LEAD HUMANITY TO ITS DOOM.
item.dc:creator: DrasarSalman
item.description:
If the world would go under in 24 hours, I would just play computer games for 23 hours and watch a sunset, the news or something else… and laugh.

If the world really would have come to an end, I would have used my last time on earth to shoot myself. A bullet from temple to temple would give a millisecond of pain and then cut most of the crucial nerve connections in the brain. It would be better than getting burned, drowning, falling or having another death with pain in longer than 1 milliseconds!
